snippet.title: The Photographer - Trailer
snippet.description:
The Photographer is an atmospheric survival-horror game. You are a crime scene photographer who needs to take pictures of the criminal case involving the Edwards family. The house where it occurred feels eerie and you already know that there is something that does not want you to be here…

Play it now on Itch.io: https://crowmountaingames.itch.io/the-photographer

Join my Discord server: https://discord.gg/MFp6Kas7fc
